                <h1>How to Easily Change Your iPhone Wallpaper</h1>
                <p>Changing your iPhone wallpaper can refresh your device's look and feel. To change it, go to Settings > Wallpaper > Choose a New Wallpaper. You can select from dynamic, stills, or your photos. Once you’ve picked the perfect image, set it as your Lock Screen, Home Screen, or both for a personalized touch that reflects your style!</p>
